# Keep secrets and bulk out of the Docker build context (the Rust images do `COPY . .`).
# Secret hygiene first: .env must NEVER enter an image layer (CLAUDE.md §2, SECRETS-AND-DATABASE.md).
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
*.key
*.pem
secrets/

# Build artifacts and VCS — large and unneeded inside the build.
target/
.git/
.github/

# Local data / object store / DB dumps — never bake into an image.
data/
pgdata/
*.dump
*.sql.gz

# Python extractor local cruft (its build context is services/extractor/).
**/__pycache__/
**/*.pyc
.venv/
